#include <cstdio>
#include <string.h>

{

            count+=1;

        {

            {
                if(co[i][0]==a&&co[i][1]==b){
                flag[i]=0;
                break;}
            }
        }
        if(strcmp(s,"get")==0)
        {int i=0;

            while(i<count+1)

                    bigx=co[i][0];
                    y=co[i][1];
                    t=1;}
                i+=1;
            }if(t==1)

            {

                countx+=1;

            {int i=0;
                while(i<count+1)
            {
                if(co[i][1]>b&&co[i][1]<bigy&&flag[i]==1){
                    bigy=co[i][1];
                    x=co[i][0];}
                i+=1;
            }if(i<count+1)
            county+=1;
            }
            if(countx==0&&county==0)
            printf("-1\n");
            else if(countx==1)
            printf("%d %d\n",bigx,y);
            else
            printf("%d %d\n",x,bigy);
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
